HEADWORD: Absoluteness
<hw>Ab"so*lute*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of being
absolute; independence of everything extraneous; unlimitedness; absolute
power; independent reality; positiveness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Absolution</ent>⟦br⟧
